text: Ethan William Childress (born February 13, 2009 in Las Vegas, Nevada) is an american actor. He is best known for his work in movies and television. Movies and programs he has starred in include: * Diary of a Wimpy Kid * Mixed-ish * The United States of Tomorrow * Miszmasz * Diary of a Wimpy Kid: Rodrick Rules (2022 movie) * Diary of a Wimpy Kid (animated movie series) == Other websites == * Category:2009 births Category:Living people Category:Actors from Las Vegas
title: Ethan William Childress
